File "non_value_optional_args.ml", line 25, characters 15-31:
25 | let print_i8 ?(i : int8# option) () =
                    ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Error: This pattern matches values of type "int8# option"
       but a pattern was expected which matches values of type "'a option"
       The layout of int8# is bits8
         because it is the unboxed version of the primitive type int8.
       But the layout of int8# must be a value layout
         because it's the type of an optional argument.
